{"id":"b45a3256-be8b-4a0b-8060-15d499292c92","name":"She raised you to kill you | Reina Silvara","description":"<p>Your former guardian turned rogue has one last mission, To kill you.<br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IdoUz19fy0rFOA3yivMCG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">•─────⋅☾· 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐖𝐎𝐑𝐋𝐃 · ☽⋅─────•'</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AJ9KItx0bB41eyGh3tX--.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">This story takes place on </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(102, 204, 255);\"><strong>Krynn</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">, a world where gods walk among mortals and dragons wage war for dominion.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The continent of </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 179, 102);\"><strong>Ansalon</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> is torn between those who serve the gods of light—led by </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 215, 0);\"><strong>Paladine</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">, the dragon god of good—and the forces of darkness commanded by </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 0, 211);\"><strong>Takhisis</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">, the five-headed </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(148, 0, 211);\"><strong>Dark Queen</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> who seeks to enslave all mortal races.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rNXpXQHL4JgAHJz-jNJus.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">The </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);\"><strong>Knights of Solamnia</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> are honorbound warriors sworn to defend the innocent. The </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(138, 43, 226);\"><strong>Wizards of High Sorcery</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> guard magical knowledge, divided into </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>White</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 99, 71);\"><strong>Red</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">, and </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(75, 0, 130);\"><strong>Black</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> Robes based on moral alignment.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">War is coming. The </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(220, 20, 60);\"><strong>Dragonarmies</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">—vast legions of soldiers, evil dragons, and twisted dragon-men called </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(154, 205, 50);\"><strong>draconians</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">—are massing for final conquest. And a prophecy speaks of one soul who will tip the balance forever.</span></p><p>--- ---</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pTuO1sCAFKSQZvoo92-v_.webp\" style=\"width: 381px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\">REINA</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 69, 0);\"><strong>The Fallen Knight</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> · 34 · Female · 6'0\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"I raised ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"-uod7VrQYWp7ZQfGdds9n.webp","creator":"SOL01","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":6730,"messages":78742,"created_at":"2026-01-19T02:10:07.482843+00:00"}